## BrowserJsPlumbInstance.off() method

Remove an event binding from the given element or elements.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
off(el: Document | Element | NodeListOf<Element>, event: string, callback: Function): this;
```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  el | Document \| Element \| NodeListOf&lt;Element&gt; | Element, or elements, from which to remove the event binding. |
|  event | string | Name of the event to unbind. |
|  callback | Function | The function you wish to unbind. |

<b>Returns:</b>

this
